\is1 Introduction
\ip \bk The first sulat of Pidru\bk*, insulat din for of believers nekegsuwey-suwey nangugpe there dapit of Asya Minur. The tuyu of Pidru of migsulat here, the pegbagget of believers keilangan eglig‑en sikandan taliware of masumpit pegbayad-bayad kandan tenged of pegpalintutuu ran. Impasuman-suman sikandan of Pidru concerning the kaluwasan dan, of kamatayen of Hisu Kristu, of pegkeuyag din and of return din. Su nanengnengan of Pidru emun ke iyan dan layun egsumsumanen the egpallatengen dan there to langit, egkaantus dan iya the langun difficulty here of ampew of tane. Impanengneng din again sikandan emun ke egkeehet the pegpalintutuu ran pinaahi of peg-antus dan of me difficulty and me kalasayan, egpakarawat sikandan of dasag of “Timpu igpakite e si Hisu Kristu.” (1:7,13)
\ip Migbanasalan din again sikandan keilangan eg-ay-ayaran dan the batasan dan isip me keet-etawan of Kristu, and keilangan also egparuma-ruma sikandan of seeye se due katenged egmandu kandan.
\iot Main components of this “book”
\io1 Introduction \ior 1:1-2\ior*
\io1 The pegpasuman-suman concerning the kaluwasan ware katamanan \ior 1:3-12\ior*
\io1 The pegbanasal concerning the peg-ugpe matulus \ior 1:13–2:10\ior*
\io1 The pegparuma-ruma ta of seeye se due me katenged there to kanta \ior 2:11–3:7\ior*
\io1 The tambag concerning the egginguma me difficulty \ior 3:8–4:19\ior*
\io1 The tambag for of pangulu and of believers \ior 5:1-11\ior*
\io1 The me pangemusta \ior 5:12-14\ior*
